Special Notes for Game Developers
Educational Use: Teachers and students are encouraged to use and modify this code for learning purposes. Credit to the original authors is appreciated but not required in academic settings.
Modding Community: You are welcome to create mods, extensions, or total conversions of VlaTank. Please share your creations with the community!
Porting: Porting to other platforms (mobile, consoles, web) is permitted for non-commercial projects. For commercial ports, please contact the copyright holders.
Asset Creation: If you create new assets (art, sound, music) for VlaTank, you retain copyright to your creations. By contributing them to the project, you grant a perpetual license for their use within VlaTank.

